{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-note-template-js","path":"/brass pen/","result":{"pageContext":{"id":"c2b3e4ad-ca80-520f-8829-689471c2f1f1","html":"<h1>brass pen</h1>\n<p><em>june 2025</em></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f72d45781f8493d56c8d3b6d84bddfc9/d3c45/brass-pen.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.1081081081081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"a brass tube pen\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f72d45781f8493d56c8d3b6d84bddfc9/1c72d/brass-pen.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f72d45781f8493d56c8d3b6d84bddfc9/a80bd/brass-pen.jpg 148w,\n/static/f72d45781f8493d56c8d3b6d84bddfc9/1c91a/brass-pen.jpg 295w,\n/static/f72d45781f8493d56c8d3b6d84bddfc9/1c72d/brass-pen.jpg 590w,\n/static/f72d45781f8493d56c8d3b6d84bddfc9/a8a14/brass-pen.jpg 885w,\n/static/f72d45781f8493d56c8d3b6d84bddfc9/fbd2c/brass-pen.jpg 1180w,\n/static/f72d45781f8493d56c8d3b6d84bddfc9/d3c45/brass-pen.jpg 3472w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>i somewhat spontaneously bought a bunch of little brass and tin parts from blick and then i figured that a g7 ink well would probably fit in them.'</p>\n<p>so i made an arrangement and started supergluing things together and it worked!</p>\n<p>not pictured, but later on for accent i put some leftover veneer on part of the barrel and the end cap.</p>\n<p>funny thing is i lost this recently so maybe it shall come back into my life at some later serendipitous date.</p>"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}